  Locus:
    Page: 67
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Consciousness
---
A lake that is absolutely calm gives to you a perfect reflection. The
moment it becomes disturbed in the least, the reflection is distorted; and
if the agitation is increased, the reflection will be completely lost. Your
consciousness is the lake.
